      <title>寻求价值交易者在我们的飞行中增加巴西的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/value-seeking-traders-boost-brazil-stocks-in-flight-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2022年以来的第一季度，巴西股票正在关闭，因为投资者从波动的美国市场撤退，在其他地方寻求便宜的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/value-seeking-traders-boost-brazil-stocks-in-flight-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 14:43:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯原油的威胁时，石油的进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）建议美国可能努力减少俄罗斯的原油运输之后，石油上升了，俄罗斯是世界第三大生产商和主要出口商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票下沉，当关税加油冲向债券时：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票在世界各地下降，债券攀升，黄金创下了另一个纪录，贸易商为唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税公告做好了准备，这引起了人们对更广泛的贸易战争的担忧，因为经济表现出放缓的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国征收避风港时，黄金首次上涨了$ 3,100</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金在本周开始时以新的纪录开始，这是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统预期的下一次关税推出，这引起了人们对全球贸易战的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
